###640e0e|**⚠️ Content Warning:** Depictions of deteriorating mental state.##

**SCP-7504 - "Sunrise, Sunset" by [[*user Mew-ltiverse]] and [[*user Greyve]]**

//Have you ever wondered what would happen if you didn't fall asleep?//

For more by us, check out [*http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/dr-mews-personnel-file Mew's stuff] and the [*https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/greyve-author-page Greyve Page]. Thanks for reading!
[[include :scp-wiki:info:end]]

[[include :scp-wiki:component:info-cw]]
